{"word":"οὐαί","slug":"οὐαί","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>οὐαί</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ Lat.\">Lat.</a> vae, a cry of pain]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> as interjection expressing sense of profound grief, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ esp.\">esp.</a> in face of impending disaster <b>woe, alas! <a href='B:470 11:21'>Mt 11:21</a>; <a href='B:470 18:7'>18:7</a>; <a href='B:480 14:21'>Mk 14:21</a>; <a href='B:490 6:24-26'>Lk 6:24-26</a>; <a href='B:490 17:1'>17:1</a>; <a href='B:490 21:23'>21:23</a>; <a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 11</a>; <a href='B:730 12:12'>Rv 12:12</a></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ al.\">al.</a> <b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> as noun <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on certainty of assured disaster <b>woe <a href='B:530 9:16'>1 Cor 9:16</a>; <a href='B:730 9:12'>Rv 9:12</a>; <a href='B:730 11:14'>11:14</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐά\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:οὐδαμῶς\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}